        <h2>Branding</h2>
        <h3>Logo Options</h3>
        <div class="gap-v gap-h gallery-3-col">
            <img src="img/case-studies/cft/cftLogoOption1.svg"
                alt="Logo option for Cards for Today based on the Bicycle Cards packaging">
